LINUX NOTES


:: shows first / last 10 lines from specified line

head /link/to/file
tail /link/to

::shows first 5
head -n5 file 

::filter by age of creation (earliest first)
ls -t

:: first 4 earliest files
ls -t | head -n4 

::display / search (will allow you to do a lot of stuff...)
run comand | less

::read less manual
man less

::how to enable sass
sass —watch styles.sass:styles.css
OR watch the whole dir
sass —-watch sass:css

::how to install bourbon to project directory
bourbon install --path sass/0-plugins/


